{
  "stem": "8786.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they brought in Germans to, to clean up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Americans were, in my opinion, very soft with these monsters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because they should have-- they should have done to them what they did to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were very soft with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I remember that they brought in some SSes from the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And one of the men, she said, no, you can do with him what you want.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I said to myself, I'm going to-- there was one guy over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He used a, a, a verse from, from, from Tehillim, from the Psalms, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But he, he was kicking him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I didn't, didn't have the strength, or, or not, not the ambitions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was-- it was against my basic nature to go and kick a human being, even though it was animal-like, they were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In Wels, I-- God was with me, over there, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "What happened to me, I throw away all my clothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I got dressed [LAUGHS] in a SS uniform, in a SS uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It was the-- the hat was twice the size of my-- of my head, the hat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I'm walking on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I see a whole group of people are coming toward me-- an American soldier.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They caught some SSes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he stops me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's a Jewish boy, a Jewish American soldier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he wanted to find out if I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said it to him in German that he should kiss my-- he should kiss [LAUGHS] my foot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't-- I didn't understand what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just saw that the SS was bending down and kissing my foot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This happened in Wels.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, I have here a paper from Wels.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
